&lt;li&gt;Ensure patients feel comfortable, informed, and cared for throughout their visit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anticipate provider and team needs to maintain efficient studio flow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with teammates to deliver a seamless, high-quality patient experience&lt;/li&gt;
