&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver outstanding chairside support to dentists and/or hygienists across a variety of procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure patients feel comfortable, informed, and cared for throughout their visit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anticipate provider and team needs to maintain efficient studio flow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with teammates to deliver a seamless, high-quality patient experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Operatory &amp;amp; Clinical Excellence (All Assistants)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and maintain treatment rooms, instruments, and equipment in compliance with OSHA and CDC standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage sterilization workflows and maintain a safe, clean clinical environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take dental radiographs and support accurate, complete patient records (as permitted by role and experience)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Supporting Dentists (Dental Assistant Focus)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide chairside support across a full range of general and specialty procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with dentists to support clinical excellence and productivity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to studio performance goals through efficiency, preparedness, and teamwork&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Supporting Hygienists (Hygiene Assistant Focus)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
